    slug: 'retail-shoplifting-organised-crime-impact',
    title: 'Organised Retail Crime Costing UK Shops £1.8bn/Year: Detection and Response',
    metaDescription: 'Organised retail crime is costing UK shops £1.8 billion per year. Here is how SMB retailers detect, prevent, and respond to organised shoplifting — with real figures and practical steps.',
    cluster: 'Business Resilience',
